caption.text: Farewell dinner with UQ exchange students

Tagged by @xjanechristiex for the #20factsaboutme challenge. Here goes:

1. Libra
2. AB+
3. Firstborn; with a younger brother who looks nothing like me (cc: @stanleytjokro).
4. Buddhist
5. A clinical psychologist in the making at FPsi UI-UQ.
6. Unlike most people, I don't miss HS, just the friends.
7. I hate being a minority, but it's not like I would just move to Taiwan and start speaking 中文。
8. Dream of living in the UK one day.
9. Occasionally mistaken as a Japanese.
10. A skeptic & cynic
11. Overthinker; which is why it's hard for me to make up my mind.
12. I've tried many activities but can't settle on one to master... so I've sort of given up on that.
13. My friends say I randomly jump from one topic to another during conversations.
14. INTJ
15. I always plan ahead, and get annoyed when something interrupts my schedule.
16. Have wanted another pet dog since Orleen died of old age, but mom doesn't want to re-experience the sadness of losing another pet.
17. I love reading; my favorite book so far is Change of Heart, written by my favorite author Jodi Picoult.
18. Favorite movie: The Vow
19. I enjoy crafting during hols.
20. Braided hair 🎀💗
To those I tagged, it's your turn!
